snippet.title: Office Dating Simulator 2020: Gold Edition - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Ever wanted to date a giant rat? Bake a cheesecake with a potted plant? Commit credit card fraud? Burn your corporate hellhole workplace to the ground? It's time to discover a budding office romance in Office Dating Simulator 2020: Gold Edition!

This brand-new release of the game features full voice acting, animated portraits, revitalized art/sound, tons of polish, and more!

Releasing 12/31 for free: https://brainloaf.itch.io/office-dating-simulator-2020

Twitter: https://twitter.com/BrainloafStudio
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/BrainloafStudio/
Discord server: https://discord.gg/nxjcGnh
